k-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/Vj5HNqQO5FA&t=750" target="_blank"><strong># 太棒膠拆除</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/Vj5HNqQO5FA_750.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/Vj5HNqQO5FA&t=780" target="_blank"><strong># 門長度加長技巧</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/Vj5HNqQO5FA_780.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/Vj5HNqQO5FA&t=770" target="_blank"><strong># 精油與蜂蠟使用方法</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/Vj5HNqQO5FA_770.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/Vj5HNqQO5FA&t=790" target="_blank"><strong># 檜木精油塗抹</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/Vj5HNqQO5FA_790.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/Vj5HNqQO5FA&t=840" target="_blank"><strong># 蜂蠟的效果</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/Vj5HNqQO5FA_840.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/Vj5HNqQO5FA&t=1010" target="_blank"><strong># 安